title: A Game of CAT and MOUSE
body_text:
The game of cat and mouse returns at DODGEBALL 159 and you can bet all hell will break loose .. outside the home!
EastCoastDodgeball
proudly presents its third individual
Championship Chase
, and this time the stakes are high! Not only will the victor receive a truck load of bragging rights, but be heavily rewarded with a mystery prize!
In order to kick things off, the special
Player's Choice
Rimshot Contest
will decide the inaugural champion of DODGEBALL 159 as well as the rule-maker for the event itself, forming two formidable armies as he or she sees fit.
Find out who wins the "gold" on October 11 beginning at 7:15pm!

body_html:
The game of cat and mouse returns at DODGEBALL 159 and you can bet all hell will break loose .. outside the home!

EastCoastDodgeball proudly presents its third individual Championship Chase, and this time the stakes are high! Not only will the victor receive a truck load of bragging rights, but be heavily rewarded with a mystery prize!

In order to kick things off, the special Player's Choice Rimshot Contest will decide the inaugural champion of DODGEBALL 159 as well as the rule-maker for the event itself, forming two formidable armies as he or she sees fit.

Find out who wins the "gold" on October 11 beginning at 7:15pm!
